- If types are weak or missing, ask to strengthen them

## Project Structure

Each game is an independent experiment in the pyglet folder:

```
pyglet/
  game_name/
    src/
      __init__.py
      main.py
      ...
    tests/
      ...
```

Common project files in the `./pyglet` folder: `pyproject.toml`, `uv.lock`
